<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8" />
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0" />
  <title>Senior Special Programs Coordinator | William Duffy</title>

  <!-- Sans-serif font -->
  <link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Inter:wght@400;600&display=swap" rel="stylesheet">

  <style>
    :root {
      /* Bristol-inspired green palette (WCAG conscious) */
      --primary: #1B5E20;       /* dark green */
      --secondary: #2E7D32;     /* medium green */
      --background: #FFFFFF;
      --text: #1A1A1A;
      --muted: #555555;
      --accent: #E8F5E9;        /* light green background accent */
    }

    * {
      box-sizing: border-box;
      margin: 0;
      padding: 0;
    }

    body {
      font-family: 'Inter', Arial, sans-serif;
      background-color: var(--background);
      color: var(--text);
      line-height: 1.6;
      font-size: 16px;
    }

    header {
      background-color: var(--primary);
      color: #FFFFFF;
      padding: 2rem 1rem;
      text-align: center;
    }

    header h1 {
      font-size: 1.75rem;
      font-weight: 600;
    }

    header p {
      font-size: 1.1rem;
      margin-top: 0.5rem;
    }

    main {
      max-width: 800px;
      margin: 2rem auto;
      padding: 0 1rem;
    }

    section {
      margin-bottom: 2rem;
    }

    h2 {
      color: var(--primary);
      font-size: 1.25rem;
      margin-bottom: 0.5rem;
      border-bottom: 2px solid var(--accent);
      padding-bottom: 0.25rem;
    }

    p {
      margin-bottom: 0.75rem;
    }

    .muted {
      color: var(--muted);
    }

    footer {
      text-align: center;
      padding: 1rem;
      font-size: 0.9rem;
      color: var(--muted);
      border-top: 1px solid #ddd;
    }

    /* Links with sufficient contrast */
    a {
      color: var(--secondary);
    }

    a:hover {
      text-decoration: underline;
    }

    a:focus,
    button:focus {
      outline: 3px solid #FFBF47; /* high-visibility focus color */
      outline-offset: 2px;
    }

    @media (prefers-reduced-motion: reduce) {
      * {
        animation: none !important;
        transition: none !important;
      }
    }
  </style>
</head>

<body>
  <header role="banner">
    <h1>William Duffy</h1>
    <p>Senior Special Programs Coordinator<br>
    Lash Center for Teaching and Learning</p>
  </header>

  <main role="main">
    <section aria-labelledby="about">
      <h2 id="about">About</h2>
      <p>
        William Duffy serves as Senior Special Programs Coordinator at the Lash Center for Teaching and Learning.
        His work focuses on supporting academic initiatives, fostering faculty development, and enhancing student success.
      </p>
    </section>

    <section aria-labelledby="contact">
      <h2 id="contact">Contact</h2>
      <p class="muted">
        For professional inquiries, please reach out via institutional channels.
